project_descr: The project will support government efforts to develop and implement policies aimed at eradicating poverty in Namibia

outputs.output_descr: Support the Government of Namibia in its war against poverty, by developing capacity in Macro Economic Analysis and Research, by developing a blue print on wealth distribution and poverty eradication.
donor_name: US Department of State, Office to monitor & combat Tracking in persons.

outputs.output_descr: Support to El Nino Drought Emergency Response. This project supported the Government’s efforts in strengthening multi-sectoral coordination and in integration of early recovery approach in the emergency drought response initiatives in Namibia.
